blog.name: slowstrollthroughjapan
blog.title: A Slow Stroll Through Japan
blog.description: To relive the trip and share pictures I've decided to create this tumblr. It's set to auto-update a few pictures each day, and since I took over 3,000 pictures I thought it'd be a fun way of sharing and reminiscing about the trip over a fairly long period of time. Maybe by time it's done updating I'll have plans to go again!

summary: I don’t say this very often, but this speeder bike toy is my childhood. Luckily I still own mine, so I didn’t feel a need to buy...
caption:
I don’t say this very often, but this speeder bike toy is my childhood.

Luckily I still own mine, so I didn’t feel a need to buy this. I still kind of wanted to.

Anyone know what’s up with the ‘build your own stormtrooper’ in the background? I don’t have any memory of that existing and I’m usually pretty good at remember Star Wars merch.

summary: I noticed that there is a bunch of different ambients for Star Wars whether it be music ambiance or surrounding ambiance,...
body: I noticed that there is a bunch of different ambients for Star Wars whether it be music ambiance or surrounding ambiance, however, I also noticed that there is neither ambiance for Eriadu. I could imagine what the Carrion Plateau would sound like with the veermonks for surrounding ambiance, but what would the music ambiance sound like?

summary: Every time I watch a Star Wars movie, I remember why I prefer Trek.
body:
Every time I watch a Star Wars movie, I remember why I prefer Trek.

Most of the good characters either die or turn evil in Star Wars and it feels very bleak most of the time.
